              "TradeItemDescriptionInformation": {
                "AdditionalTradeItemDescription": [
                  {
                    "LanguageCode": "en",
                    "Value": "The Low-Profile Gastrostomy Replacement Tube (G. Button) Kit with the main component being the G. Button. The G. Button is a silicone feeding device comprised of a body,\ntwo‑lumen shafts, and a retaining balloon. The G. Button body has two ports and a strap with a cap. The first port with a feeding ring and duckbill valve connected to the lumen\nfor feeding and or medication. The second port with an inflation valve is connected to the lumen for balloon inflation. The device is translucent with an X-Ray line (silicone base\nwith BaSO4 - Barium sulphate) for X-ray determination of the tube position in the patient body.\nThe device is packed with accessories into a kit"
                  }
